org.pepstock.charba.client.data

Interface HasPointFillStrokeStyles

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LineDataset, LiningDataset, RadarDataset, ScatterDataset, StackedAreaDataset, TimeSeriesLineDataset, VerticalLineDataset

    public interface HasPointFillStrokeStyles
    This is an interface to set a dataset has container of fill and stroke style based on point background and border color.
    Out of the box ONLY LiningDataset has implemented this interface
    Author:
    Andrea "Stock" Stocchero

    • Method Summary
